<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="5">Pull-Ups</h3>



<p><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/pull-up" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Pull-ups</a> are similar to a traditional lat pulldown but you get the advantage of using body weight. You can even have a pull-up bar at home! Grab the bar with a shoulder-width overhand grip (hands placed on the bar shoulder distance apart, palms facing away from you) and pull yourself up as high as you can.</p>



