<h2 class="wp-block-heading list-start">Lat Muscle Anatomy And Function&nbsp;</h2>



<p>The anatomy of the lat muscle is complex and very multi-faceted due to both the large thoracic area it covers and its several different functions.&nbsp;</p>



<p>It performs five major functions around the thorax and shoulder joints, as it is a huge muscle in both presence and importance.</p>


